# User Stories – Smart Habit & Productivity Tracker

## 1. User Registration
As a new user, I want to create an account using my username, email, and password so that I can access the app features.

## 2. User Login
As a registered user, I want to log into the app using my email and password so that I can access my personalized dashboard.

## 3. View Home Screen
As a logged-in user, I want to view my list of habits on the home screen so that I can track my daily progress.

## 4. Add New Habit
As a user, I want to add new habits so that I can track additional goals.

## 5. View Habit Details
As a user, I want to view detailed information about a selected habit so that I can understand my progress.

## 6. Save Favorites
As a user, I want to mark habits as favorites so that I can quickly access important habits.

## 7. Data Persistence
As a user, I want my habits to be saved locally so that my data remains even after closing the app.

## 8. API Integration
As a user, I want to see motivational quotes fetched from an external API so that I stay motivated.

## 9. Notifications
As a user, I want to receive daily reminder notifications so that I do not forget to complete my habits.
